    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty intense way to put it... \"systemic theft\" and \"racial caste system.\" i like the strength of the language for the essay, but what about the counterarguments? like, how would someone who believes in strict meritocracy or individual responsibility respond to this, and how can i frame their view in the essay so it doesn't make my main argument look weak?",
